review_blob: Oh My God. I go to this brewary every time at christmas, and have always been impressed with thier beers. This is definetly my favorite. Great passion fruit flavor, but not too sweet. Very refreshing wheat beer, goes down easy. I hope this one stays around for a while.
750 ml. bottle from rare beer club. Great champagne like beer. Drank on New years instead of champagne. Lots of citrisy hops in this one, awesome flavor.
750ml bottle from rare beer club. One of the most amazing beers I have tried. Tastes like your deinking candy. Ive got some of this aging at my house. Mmmmmmm.
